### Variables

@baseUrl = localhost:3004

@contentType = application/json



# basic request
http://{{baseUrl}}


### Get all Tasks
GET http://{{baseUrl}}/api/tasks


### Get one Task
GET http://{{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}


### Create a new task
# @name createTask
POST http://{{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "title": "Learn the Nest2 from http visual code 3",
    "description": "Complete the NestJS course",
    "status": "OPEN"
}
### Set the task id
@taskId = {{createTask.response.body.id}}

### update a task

PATCH http://{{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "status": "DONE"
}

 
### Delete a task

Delete http://{{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
 
 
 